🚨Escócia 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿: Ativistas ambientais do grupo “Just stop oil” na cidade de Aberdeen, jogaram tinta em uma agência do banco Barclays nesta segunda-feira (14). 
Os ativistas exigem que o banco corte financiamentos de empresas que utilizam combustíveis fósseis

🇨🇳🔥🦠📹 — Rejection of COVID Zero Policy? | Over the past 48 hours, Riots and mass protests in Mainland China's Guangzhou, the Heart of the Cantonese region of PRC-Controlled Guangdong are being reported on Chinese clusters of social medias against the Lockdown policies implemented by PRC Govt

On videos shared by netizens and activists, it's possible to see the Cantonese citizens attacking local health officials, as well as wrecking government cars and smashing PCR checkpoints

As expected, the Mainland Internet regulators were quickly to suppress any information flowing outside the country.

Such protests were heavily celebrated by the factions of the Chinese Opposition - From Cantonese Separatists and Guo Wengui's Federalists to Liberals of the so-called "Great Translators Movement" and Falun Gong Cultists - on social medias
